    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research to support device submission; the assessment team accepts the evidence package as sufficient for the stated decision.",
